    <p>Every woman has a story. For some women, that includes working in a field all day in 90ºF weather and only making a dollar. Shift's goal is to help women in extreme poverty around the world reach a level of financial stability through mobile cash transfers and educational programs in financial literacy. The program is comprised of 5 phases (Mobilization, Sponsorship, Banking, Investment, and Empowerment) that provide finicial solutions to communities of women to jumpstart their financial stability and ulimately make a difference at home, their community, and society.</p>
