    <p>The color palette, gradients, and typographic system reflect the strength and femininity of the women in need. The composition is laid out to tell a story so users can connect to the women in these communities and follow along thier Shift journey toward finacialy stability. The company's founder, Tricia, took a series of inpsirational photos during her trip to Africa that served as the focal point of this narrative. When donating, users can visually see the value of their donation—the amount corresponds to items like food for their families to funding a woman's education.</p>
